title: Winning numbers drawn in 'Cash 5' game
maintext:
ROCKY HILL, Conn. (AP) _ The winning numbers in Friday evening’s drawing of the Connecticut Lottery’s “Cash 5” game were:
15-23-26-32-33
(fifteen, twenty-three, twenty-six, thirty-two, thirty-three)
